# {{ ip }}_verif — UVM verification environment for `{{ ip }}`

Generated by **uvm-gen v{{ tool_version }}** from `cfg/{{ input_basename }}`
(configuration `{{ config_name }}`, param hash `{{ param_hash }}`).
Everything here is yours to edit — **re-running uvm-gen never overwrites
