except `verif_matrix.yaml`, which is verification history).

## Quick start

```bash
cd sim
make compile                                # elaborate-only sanity (stub DUT)
make run TEST={{ ip }}_smoke_test           # reset + traffic, UVM_ERROR count 0
make run TEST={{ ip }}_smoke_test PASSIVE=1 # SoC-reuse check: all agents passive
make waves TEST={{ ip }}_smoke_test         # + SHM waveform probing
make matrix                                 # verification status per configuration
```

Xcelium only: single-step `xrun`, bundled UVM-1.2 (`-uvmhome CDNS-1.2`).

